'''Justice''' was a [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunter]] who had a "pet" named [[Truth]]. [[Gender/Legends|He]] was known to have visited a bar called [[Maizie's]] on the planet [[Mandrine/Legends|Mandrine]] at least once, where he met with [[Captain/Legends|Captain]] [[Scarlet Bloodhawk]].

